  "description": "<b>虚拟现实和全息图投影供应商<a href=\"http://www.domusweb.it/en/design/2013/06/10/workaholic_holograms.html\" target=\"_blank\">Domus</a>今天展示了一种用于机场的全息图迎宾技术，它可以帮助乘客登机并宣讲安全常识，减少人力成本。</b>据称美国多个机场已经开始安装这种系统。同时全息技术还允许利用类似Siri的方式来与乘客沟通。这种技术还可以用于博物馆、零售商店甚至医生办公室。现在的问题是，遇到全息图迎宾，您还会微笑回应么？<img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2d5ec70d/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241328.htm&amp;t=%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BD%E6%9C%BA%E5%9C%BA%E5%BC%80%E5%A7%8B%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E5%85%A8%E6%81%AF%E5%9B%BE%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E8%AE%A9%E8%99%9A%E6%8B%9F%E4%BA%BA%E7%89%A9%E8%BF%8E%E5%AE%BE\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241328.htm&amp;t=%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BD%E6%9C%BA%E5%9C%BA%E5%BC%80%E5%A7%8B%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E5%85%A8%E6%81%AF%E5%9B%BE%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E8%AE%A9%E8%99%9A%E6%8B%9F%E4%BA%BA%E7%89%A9%E8%BF%8E%E5%AE%BE\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241328.htm&amp;t=%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BD%E6%9C%BA%E5%9C%BA%E5%BC%80%E5%A7%8B%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E5%85%A8%E6%81%AF%E5%9B%BE%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E8%AE%A9%E8%99%9A%E6%8B%9F%E4%BA%BA%E7%89%A9%E8%BF%8E%E5%AE%BE\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241328.htm&amp;t=%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BD%E6%9C%BA%E5%9C%BA%E5%BC%80%E5%A7%8B%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E5%85%A8%E6%81%AF%E5%9B%BE%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E8%AE%A9%E8%99%9A%E6