  "description": "<b>Foursquare等社交网络服务可以让你跟踪朋友的行踪，但每个人总会有逃离现实社会的想法，社交焦虑让你有那么几天可能会想抛开你所有的朋友一个人静一静，</b>这个时候开发人员Scott Garner研制的Hell is Other People应用就可以根据你朋友的位置帮助你计算出一个完美的位置，可以几乎避免所有朋友接触。这个位置被称为“最佳疏远安全区”。这款应用现在还在实验阶段，下面是一些图像：<img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2d5ea1fb/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241327.htm&amp;t=%E5%8F%8D%E7%A4%BE%E4%BA%A4%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8Hell+is+Other+People%E5%B8%AE%E4%BD%A0%E9%81%BF%E5%BC%80%E6%9C%8B%E5%8F%8B\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241327.htm&amp;t=%E5%8F%8D%E7%A4%BE%E4%BA%A4%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8Hell+is+Other+People%E5%B8%AE%E4%BD%A0%E9%81%BF%E5%BC%80%E6%9C%8B%E5%8F%8B\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241327.htm&amp;t=%E5%8F%8D%E7%A4%BE%E4%BA%A4%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8Hell+is+Other+People%E5%B8%AE%E4%BD%A0%E9%81%BF%E5%BC%80%E6%9C%8B%E5%8F%8B\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241327.htm&amp;t=%E5%8F%8D%E7%A4%BE%E4%BA%A4%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8Hell+is+Other+People%E5%B8%AE%E4%BD%A0%E9%81%BF%E5%BC%80%E6%9C%8B%E5%8F%8B\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241327.htm&amp;t=%E5%8F%8D%E7%A4%BE%E4%BA%A4%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8Hell+is+Other+People%E5%B8%AE%E4%BD%A0%E9%81%BF%E5%BC%80%E6%9C%8B%E5%8F%